---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white border-b border-brand-border/40">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="How We Work"
      description="We follow a clear, practical process to turn ideas and raw content into working learning systems."
    />

    <div class="relative">
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-brand-border/60 transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>

        <div class="space-y-12">

            <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-center md:text-right mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">1. Audit</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We review your content, course idea, platform, learner goals, and launch needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-accent border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-center md:text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">2. Structure</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We organize your knowledge into a course map, modules, lessons, outcomes, and learner journey.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-center md:text-right mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">3. Create</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We help produce or convert learning assets such as scripts, worksheets, quizzes, summaries, resources, and onboarding content.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">4</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-center md:text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">4. Build</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We support Kajabi, LMS, course website, funnel, email, automation, and student access setup.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

             <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-center md:text-right mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">5. Launch</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We prepare the system for leads, checkout, students, onboarding, and delivery.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">5</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm hidden md:flex text-white font-bold text-sm">6</div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 text-center md:text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">6. Improve</h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-textMain">We support updates, QA, content improvements, and future launches.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
